code: @Test public void testInjectorIsDefaultByDefault() throws Exception {     Injector injector = context.getInjector().     assertIsInstanceOf(DefaultInjector.class, injector). }

@Test public void testNewInstance() throws Exception {     Injector injector = context.getInjector().     MyFoo foo = injector.newInstance(MyFoo.class).     foo.setName("Claus").     MyFoo foo2 = injector.newInstance(MyFoo.class).     assertNotSame(foo, foo2).     assertEquals("Claus", foo.getName()).     assertNull(foo2.getName()). }
